  “Pa-pah, ma-mah, kin2 pi7-pan7 oh! Pai3-tng5 e5 cheng-siaN teh tan5-lah-ne7!” Hui7-bi2 e5 sim chin hoaN-hi2: in-ui7 kin-mi5 si7 Kiu3-chu2-tan3. I kap in hiaN-ko Teng-liong5 chu7 kui2-na7 tiam2-cheng cheng5, chiu7 saN-khou3 oaN7 pian7-pian7, tak8-hang7 chun2-pi7 cheng2-che5 beh khi3 hu3. Hui7-bi2 kin-ni5 19 hoe3 tu2 ti7 Ko-tiong 3 lian5, koh chit8 hak8-ki5 e7 pit8-giap8. SeN choe3 siu3-khi3, oah8-tang7, leng2-li7. I e5 tek8-tiong5 chiu7-si7 im-gak8, gau5 toaN5 kng3-khim5, siaN ia7 chin sui2, chhiuN3 khi2-lai5 oan2-ju5 gim5-leng5. Ji5-chhiaN2 oan2-choan2 chheng-chhui3. Si7 thian-seng e5 chu-chit, chiong-lai5 iu2-bong7 e5 im-gak8-ka. Teng-liong5 si7 thak8 Tai7-hak8 siong-kho, ia7-si7 chit8 e5 siu3-chai5, Kin-ni5 24 hoe3, chhu3-bi7 im-gak8 kap phau2-be2. Koh chit8-ki5 ia7 e7 pit8-giap8. In-tau si7 li7 Chiang-chiu koan7-siaN5 jip8-soaN iok 5, 6 phou3-lou7 e5 soaN-kha, si7 chit8 e5 sio2-sio2 e5 ke-chhi7. Jin5-khau2 iok-liok8 3, 4 chheng lang5. Chian5-chheng si5-tai7 bat tui3 hia chhut kui2-na7 e5 ki2-jin5, siu3-chai5 ia7 be7 chio2, sou2-i2 lang5 chheng hit e5 ke-a2 kio3 choe3 Su7-liong5-ke. Ke sui-jian5 se3-se3 khiok u7 chit8 choa7 ke-a2-lou7, u7 che7-che7 tiam3, be7 hi5 bah long2 u7. Lan2 e5 pai3-tng5 si7 ti7 ke-a2-thau5, kui-bou5 put-chi2 toa7, si7 chit8 keng tong5-hong5 e5 iuN5-koan2. Ti7 lau5-teng2 le2-pai3, lau5-e7 choe3 Chu2-jit8-oh8. Bok8-su-koan2 khi2-tit chin-sui2, ti7 chit e5 soaN-kha na2-chun2 chin bo5 su3-phoe3 e5 khoan2. M7-ku2 ki5-sit8 chit keng kau3-hoe7 si7 chin heng. Mui2-le2-pai3 chit8-pou iok 300 goa7 lang5 le2-pai3. Chia si7 chit8 e5 soaN-hoe3 e5 chhut-jip8-khau2. Che7-che7 hiaN-ti7 si7 tui3 soaN-lai7 chhut-lai5 le2-pai3. Chia thiN-khi3 liang5, keng2-ti3 ho2, joah8-thiN se-iuN5 soan-kau3-su siong5-siong5 lai5 chia hioh-khun3, kau3-hoe7 ia7 u7 hu7-siat chit8 keng pin5-bin5 e5 chin2-liau5-sou2, hoan7-chia2 ia7 chin-che7. Ong5 Bok8-su e5 thoan5-to7-li2, Li2 i-seng e5 i-piN7 long2 chin chhut-mia5. 
  Hui7-bi2 e5 lau7-pe7 ia7-si7 chit8 e5 lau7 siu3-chai5, i e5 kong bat pai3-beng7 koe3 Chiang-chiu koan7-tiuN2. Sng3 si7 chit8 e5 bun5-bek8 e5 se3-ka. Kho2-sioh lau7 siu3-chai5 cha2 bat chiah8 a-phian3, ji5-chhiaN2 koh hoN3 phiau5, tou2, im2. Sou2-i2 ke-hoe2 ui7 i phoa3 khi3 chin-che7. Tng oa2 40 hoe3 peN7 chit8 e7 hiam2-si2, khi3 jip8 koan7-siaN5 lan2 kau3-hoe7 e5 i-koan2, tui3 an2-ni m7-na7 peN7 ho2, soa3 koe2 a-phian3. Siang7 hoaN-hi2 e5 chiu7-si7 tit-tioh8 to7-li2 sin3 Ia5-sou. Hit-si5 Hui7-bi2 iok 7, 8 hoe3, Teng-liong5 iok 12 hoe3. Au7-lai5 na2 jiat8-sim chiu7 siu7 keng2 choe3 TiuN2-lo2. Kau3-taN lian5-lian5 tiong7-jim7. Ti7 chit e5 se3-se3 e5 te7-hng siu3-chai5 Lim5 tiuN2-lo2 tai7-ke to bat--i. 
  Tui3 seN chit tui3 kiaN2 liau2-au7 long2 bo5 koh u7 se3-kiaN2, sou2-i2 nng7-lau7 thiaN3 mia7-mia7. I bo5 choe3 seng-li2, i keng-eng5 long5-giap8, chiong sou2 u7 kui2-kah chui2-chhan5 chhiaN3 tng5-kang lai5 choh. I sui-jian5 si7 bun5-sin iau2-ku2 chin u7 gian2-kiu3 sim, i e5 tiu7-a2, a2-si7 beh8-a2 long2 bat siu7 seng2 long5-hoe7 siuN2. M7-na7 keng-long5 tui3 chhi7 gu5, iuN5, ti to chin u7 gian2-kiu3, koh ia7 ka-ti7 khui hi5-ti5 pang3-hi5. Ti7 au7-bin7 oa2 soaN e5 koe2-chi2 theh8 sou2 cheng3 e5 kam-a2 ia7 chin sui2. I chai han-chu5 keng toa7-ti. Koh chhi7 gu5 khioh tui-pui5, put-lun7 tui-pui5-sia3 e5 kian3-cho7, tak8-hang7 chin hap8-li2. I e5 pui5 chhiong-chiok, tui3 thou2-te7 chhim keng, si-pui5 sek-hap8. I e5 gou7-kak tak8-ni5 to pi2 lang5 khah ho2 siu. Chhek siok8 e5 si5 chhi7 che7-che7 ke, ah seN nng7. Go5, ah ti7 hi5-ti5 pang3-sai2, khut u7 pui5 hi5 gau5 toa7. Bo5-lun7 peN5-bin7, lip8-the2 e5 long5-giap8 i to siuN7 e7 kau3. Ti7 i au7-piah ia7 u7 chap8 goa7 kah e5 soaN cheng3 siuN-si sio hoe2-thoaN3, ia7 u7 cheng3 che7-che7 e7 choe3-tit liau7 e5 chhiu7, si7 chit8 e5 gau5 phah-sng3 e5 lang5. Siong7-te3 toa7-toa7 siuN2-su3 i, kau3-hoe7 e5 keng-che3 i ia7 kek8-lek8 chi-chhi5 chin-chiaN3 si7 Siong7-te3 ho2 e5 koan2-ke. 
  TaN Teng-liong5 kap sio-moai7 Hui7-bi2 tng ti7 hioh ni5 to3-lai5 e7 tit choe3-hoe2 khi3 hu3 Seng3-tan3 iu5-ge7-hoe7 si7 12 hun e5 hoaN-hi2. Kin-mi5 nng7 hiaN-moai7 beh piau2-ian2 kng3-khim5 tok8-chau3, kap hiaN-ko e5 sio2-the5-khim5 tok8-chau3, kap hap8-chau3. Tek8-piat8 Hui7-bi2 e5 tok8-chhiuN3 Ong5 Bok8-su e5 leng7-ai3 Soat-mui5 sio2-chia2 e5 phoaN7-chau3 si7 choe3 te7-it siu7 chu3-bak8 e5 chhut-bok8. Nng7 hiaN-moai7 phok-phok-thiau3 tit8-tit8 teh tan2 pa-pa, ma-ma m7 khah-kin2 thang lai5 khi3. In-ui7 pa-pa, ma-ma lau7-lah, kiaN5-lou7 tah8-tham7 su-iau3 in choe3 phoaN7. Koh bo5-loa7-ku2 chiu7 choe3 hoe2 khi3 pai3-tng5. Hit me5-hng lang5-kheh, hoe7-iu2 boan2-tng5, ti7 chit e5 soaN-kha se3-se3 e5 ke-a2 u7 chit khoan2 e5 chu2-chhui si7 chin hi-han2. Na7 m7-si7 lan2 e5 kau3-hoe7, thang kong2 bo5 tang3 khoaN3 e5 seng7-hoe7. In nng7 hiaN-moai7 e5 piau2-ian2 kap Soat-mui5 sio2-chia2 e5 piau2-ian2 chin-chiaN3 si7 hit am3 siang7 ho2, hou7 lang5 toa7 o-lo2 e5 chiat-bok8. Soat-mui5 sio2-chia2 pi2 Hui7-bi2 ke nng7 hoe3, kin-ni5 21 hoe3, cha2 chit8-ni5 Ko-tiong i2-keng pit8-giap8, iau2 boe7 choe3 chhin, ti7 chhu3-nih pang-chan7 pe7-bu2. Le2-pai3-jit8 Chu2-jit8-oh8 iu3-ti7 kho, kap le2-pai3-sek e5 toaN5-khim5 long2 si7 i hu7-tam, chin-chiaN3 si7 ho2 lu2-tek e5 sio2-chia2. Ti7 iu5-ge7-hoe7 tiong u7 chit8-chhut kio3-cho3 “Chhoe7 po2-chu” (si7 Ia5-sou e5 phi3-ju7) choe3 khi2 chin pek-chin, chin kam2-kek lang5. Teng-liong5 khoaN3 liau2 chhim-chhim in3-siong7 ti7 nau2-lai7. Soa3 lian5-siong2 i e5 ho2 peng5-iu2 Khun-hong, chiu7-si7 cha2 i 2 ni5 tui3 in e5 bo2-hau7 pit8-giap8--e5. Hian7-chai7 si7 choe3 chu-po2 e5 chin3-chhut khau2 siong. KiaN5 kui2 na7 pai2 In3-tou7, Bian2-tian7, Siam7-lo5 put-chi2 ho2 than3, ke-hoe2 i2-keng seng5. I soa3 chu-chu siuN7 na7 toa7-oh8 pit8-giap8 tek-khak beh ka7 i choe3 chhi3 khoaN3-mai7. Iu5-ge7-hoe7 soah to3-lai5 chiong chit e5 su7 kong2 hou7 lau7-pe7 thiaN, lau7-pe7 bo5 chan3-seng5 chong2-si7 tiam7-tiam7-bo5 in3. Lau7-bo2 koh khah bo5 chan3-seng5 tit8-tit8 phoa3 chhui3-cham5. M7-ku2 Hui7-bi2 chin chan3-seng5. I kong2 chheng-lian5-lang5 eng-kai ai3 u7 mou7-hiam2 e5 cheng-sin5, eng-kai lo5-lek8 hun3-tou3, chiong-lai5 chiah u7 seng5-kong e5 ng3-bang7. 
  Nng7-lau7 khoaN3 kiaN2 long2 khi3 koh jip8-oh8, hut-jian5 kam2-kak chin bo5 lam7, ia7 siuN7 kong2 Teng-liong5 tioh8 liong7-cha2 ka7 i chhoa7, ng3-bang7 thang chou2-chi2 i khi3 hng7-hng7 keng-siong e5 liam7-thau5. Nng7-lang5 chham-siong5 liau2 chiu7 tang5-i3. SiuN7-lai5 siuN7-khi3 chiu7 siuN7 kong2 lai5 choe3 Ong5 Bok8-su e5 leng7-chhian-kim Soat-mui5 sio2-chia2. Lim5 tiuN2-lo2 chit8 e7 kong2, tiuN2-lo2-niu5 bo5 te7 2 ku3 chiu7 chan3-seng5. Tui3 an2-ni chiu7 iang-lang5 khi3 ka7 Bok8-su kong2. Ko2-jian5 si7 thian-chok chi-hap8, ia7 sia2-phoe hou7 Teng-liong5, ia7 tham3 Hui7-bi2 e5 i3-kian3. Tai7-ke long2 chan3-seng5. Soat-mui5 ia7 chin boan2-chiok chit e5 hun-su7. Tui3 an2-ni chiu7 chhiang3 le2-pai3 koaN7-tiaN7, ng3-bang7 koh kui2 goeh8-jit8 ku2 pit8-giap8 thang kiat-hun. 
  Si5-jit8 chin khoai3-koe3 koh bo5 ku2 Teng-liong5 kap Hui7-bi2 long2 pit8-giap8 to3-lai5 lah. Lim5 tiuN2-lo2 in chit8-ke m7-bian2 kong2, Ong5 Bok8-su in ia7-si7 chin hoaN-hi2. Soat-mui5 sio2-chia2 pi7-pan7 ke3-chng chin-chiaN3 bo5-eng5. 
  Lim5 tiuN2-lo2 in nng7-lau7 hoaN-hi2 kin2 ai3 khoaN3-kiN3 sun-a2, chiu7 koaN2 Teng-liong5 tioh8 kin2 kiat-hun, na7-si7 Teng-liong5 sim chu-chu siuN7 beh kap lang5 khi3 goa7-kok choe3 seng-li2, chin ai3 ka-jip8 tui7-siong. Sim long2 bo5 sim-chiaN5 ti7 kin2 kiat-hun e5 su7. Na7-si7 be7 jim2-tit ni5-lau7 e5 pe7-bo2 pek-chhiat iau3-kiu5 chiu7 chin7 hau3-to7 ti7 pit8-giap8 e5 chit8 goeh8-jit8 au7 chiu7 kiat-hun. Hit-jit8 e5 kiat-hun-sek chin-chiaN3 si7 seng7-tai7. 
  Sin-hun au7 bit8-goeh8 tiong e5 hu-hu7 chin-chiaN3 si7 tiN-bit8. Lim5 tiuN2-lo2 in nng7-lau7 ia7 chin-chiaN3 boan2-chiok. Chit8 ke chhiong-moa2 gim5-si, chhiuN3-koa kam2-sia7 e5 chhio3 siaN. U7 chit8-jit8 hut-jian5 u7 tian7-po3 lai5, chiu7-si7 Teng-liong5 sia2-phoe hou7 i e5 ho2 peng5-iu2 Khun-hong tham3 mng7 in chhut-kok e5 si5-jit8. In si7 chou-chit chit8-tui7 7 e5, to-sou3 si7 chheng-lian5, ia7 kui2 na7 e5 si7 chin lau2-lian7 e5 chong3-lian5 lang5, in koan3-si3 khia5-be2 poaN5-soaN koe3-nia2 ian5-lou7 tui3 hoa3-hoan a2-si7 sim2-mih8 soaN-lai7 e5 lang5 be2 ia2-siu3 e5 phoe5, a2-si7 chhiuN7-ge5, lok8-jiong5 tui3 soaN-nih tit8-tit8 koe3 kau3 In3-tou7 e5 toa7 tou-chhi7, u7-si5 kau3 Bian2-tian7, a2-si7 Siam7-lo5 lai5 choe3 seng-li2. Jian5-au7 chiu7 koh be2 hoe3 to3-lai5 pun2-kok chit pai2 si7 beh khi3 In3-tou7. In koat-teng7 ti7 8 goeh8 beh chhut-hoat, kau3 8 goeh8 15 beh ti7 Hun5-lam5 seng2-siaN5 hoe7-hap8. Chit-si5 u7 kong3-tian7 lai5 hou7 Teng-liong5. Teng-liong5 chiap tioh8 chit tiuN tian7 chin-chiaN3 chit8-si5 sam-sim liong2-i3. Na7 beh khi3 ia7 tng ti7 bit8-goeh8-tiong. Na7 m7-khi3 sit8-chai7 sit-loh8 ho2 ki-hoe7. I e5 pe7-bu2 si7 kek8-lek8 hoan2-tui3. Soat-mui5 chit8-sim m7-kam tiong7-hu liam-piN beh chhut-goa7 koh si7 beh khi3 hiah-hng7, chit8-sim iu7 chhiat-bong7 hu-kun seng5-kong. Hui7-bi2 thau5 kau3 boe2 si7 chan3-seng5 a-ko e5 chian5-chin3. Kau3-boe2 siuN7 kong2 m7-thang kap lang5 sit-iok, chiu7 hun3-jian5 koat-sim chhut-hoat. In chit8-tui7 7 e5, chit pai2 lian5 Teng-liong5 hap8-kiong7 u7 8 e5. Siang7 che7 hoe3 32 hoe3, choe3 tui7-tiuN2. Teng-liong5 25 hoe3 siang7 chio2-hoe3, peng5-iu2 Khun-hong 27 hoe3, tai7-ke long2 si7 chin gau5 khia5-be2 u7 lek8-liong7 e5 chheng-lian5. 
  8 goeh8 chhe 1 Teng-liong5 thau3-cha2 khi2-lai5, pi7-pan7 cheng2-che5 chiu7 beh chhut-hoat. Lau7 pe7-bu2 oa2 toa7-mng5 lau5 bak8-sai2 lai5 sang3. Ma-mah khan Teng-liong5 e5 chhiu2 chap8 teng-leng5 peh hoan-hu3 kio3 i tioh8 se3-ji7. Pe7-bo2 sang3 kau3 toa7-mng5 chiu7 theng5-pou7. HiaN-so2 sio2-kou tit8-tit8 toe3 Teng-liong5 kiaN5 kau3 chin hng7. Teng-liong5 chit8-chhiu2 khan-be2, chit8-chhiu2 khan Soat-mui5, nng7-lang5 loan5-loan5 put-sia2 m7-kam pun-khui. Au7-lai5 Hui7-bi2 theng5 kha, niu7 in 2 e5 ka-ti7 kiaN5, kau3 khah khi3 Teng-liong5 chim Soat-mui5, sim-lai7 na2-chun2 u7 kong2 be7 chhut e5 m7-kam, m7-ku2 i2-keng kap lang5 iok, koh ia7 phau7 bu5-han7 e5 kng-beng5, ng3-bang7 thang siong7-chin3 seng5-kong. Chiu7 koat-jian5 kap ai3-chhe pun-khui, phau7 chheng-lian5 lip8-chi3 chhut hiong-koan, lip8-se3 su7-giap8 put-seng5 su2 put-soan5 e5 sim-chi3, chiu7 chiuN7-be2 hui-pian tit8-tit8 phau2 chin3-cheng5 bo5 koh oat8-thau5. Soat-mui5 sim chhin-chhiuN7 beh piak-lih8, in-ui7 i bat thiaN hit tiau5 lou7 e5 gui5-hiam2, m7-na7 lou7 phaiN2 u7 toan7-gai5 choat8-phek, ji5-chhiaN2 koh u7 tok8-choa5 beng2-siu3, ia7 u7 chheN-hoan e5 chhut-chhau2. ChiN5 sui-jian5 ho2 than3, na7-si7 seN3-mia7 si7 12 hun e5 gui5-hiam2. Na2-chun2 kiat-hiong bi7-lai5 sian iu2-tiau7 e5 khoan2, sou2-i2 chit8-si5 Soat-mui5 e5 sim chhin-chhiuN7 beh piak-lih8 e5 kan-khou2, koh khoaN3 Teng-liong5 chit8 e7 chiuN7 be2, be2-piN chit8 phah be2 tit8 phau2 bo5 oat8-thau5, soa3 khui siaN khau3, sio2-kou Hui7-bi2 kin2 chau2-lai5 ka7 i an-ui3. Nng7 e5 sim bun7-bun7 saN khan to3-tng2--lai5. Hui7-bi2 khoaN3 so2-so2 e5 iu-bun7 sim ia7 soa3 seN-khi2 bu5-han7 e5 tong5-cheng5. Tauh-ti2 ko-ko m7-chai e7 peng5-an seng5-kong kau3 chhu3 a2-be7? Na7 be7, i tui3 so2-so2 kak-tit u7 chap8-ji7-ban7-hun e5 be7-tit koe3-sim, in-ui7 chit e5 su7 si7 i chit8 lang5 toa7 chan3-seng5. Sou2-i2 soa3 siuN7 bo5 oe7 thang kong2, 2 lang5 khan-chhiu2 cheng7-cheng7 kiaN5, na7-si7 Soat-mui5 na2 kiaN5 bo5 theng5 e5 chhit bak8-sai2 sim chin sim-bun