  Soat-mui5 chih tioh8 chit-tiuN phoe, chit8-sim hoaN-hi2 na2-chun2 koh kiN3 tioh8 sou2 siau3-liam7 hu-kun e5 bin7. Chiu7 chhun-chhiu2 theh8 kiaN3-tai5 teng2 kiat-hun nng7-lang5 khia7 saN pai5 sio kau-chhiu2 e5 siong7 lai5 khoaN3. Chit8-bin7 na2-chun2 sim beh piah-lih8 e5 kan-khou2, put-ti put-kak soa3 hau2 chhut--lai5. Hui7-bi2 ti7 keh-piah choe3 saN, thiaN pang5-nih u7 lang5 teh hau2 e5 siaN, koaN2-kin2 pang3 chhiu2 ka7 i tham3 khoaN3-mai7, chiu7-chai si7 in A-so2 chit8-chhiu2 theh8 a-hiaN e5 phoe, chit8-chhiu2 theh8 kap a-hiaN kiat-hun e5 siong7 teh hau2. I koaN2-kin2 chau2 jip8-khi3 kio3 A-so2...... Soat-mui5 chai sio2-kou jip8--lai5, ia7 chiu7 kin2 pang3 siong7 ti7 kiaN3-tai5, theh8 chhiu2-kin chhit bak8-sai2. Hui7-bi2 chit8-si5 ia7 siuN7 bo5 sim2-mih8 oe7 thang an-ui3 so2-so2. Chit8-bin7 ia7 chu7-chek, beh chai oe7 hou7 so2-so2 chiah-nih siong-sim lan5 koe3, chiu7 mai3 hiah-nih chek-kek8 lai5 kou2-le7 ko-ko chhut-goa7. Soa3 siuN7 kong2 ban7-it na7 u7-iaN2 u7 sim2-mih8 put-chhek e5 tai7-chi3 chek-seng5 long2 i e5. In-ui7 pe7-bo2 long2 bo5 chan3-seng5, thong ke chi2-u7 i chit8 e5 kek8-lek8 chan3-seng5. Hui7-bi2 bak8-sai2 ia7 soa3 lau5 chhut--lai5, chio so2-so2 kui7-loh8 ki5-to2. Put-ti put-kak nng7 e5 hiaN-so2 sio2-kou soa3 lam2-teh hau2. Hut-jian5 thiaN u7 kha-pou7-siaN teh lai5, chu3-i3 thiaN si7 A-pa e5 siaN, nng7 lang5 chiu7 kin2 tiam7 khi3 chhit bak8-sai2 kap A-pa chheng2-an. Lim5 tiuN2-lo2 chai in nng7-e5 tha-tu2-a2 tek-khak si7 ui7 in A-ko teh ki5-to2 lau5-bak8-sai2, in-ui7 khoaN3 in nng7-e5 bak8-chiu-phoe5 ham-ham, bak8-chiu ang5-ang5, moa2-bin7 long2 si7 lau5 bak8-sai2 e5 hun5-jiah, koh kun5 u7 kui7 loh8 thou5-kha e5 kiaN-lang5. Lau7 tiuN2-lo2 chu7-jian5 sim-lai7 ia7-si7 chin sim-bun7 khoa3-sim, chong2-si7 chit8-bin7 kho3 Siong7-te3, koh khoaN3 in nng7 hiaN-so2 sio2-kou hiah sio-thiaN3 ia7 chin siu7 an-ui3, chhui3 chiu7 teN3 chhio3-chhio3 khui-siaN an-ui3 in kong2 “Mih-sai2 hiah-nih koe3-thau5 iu-bun7, ban7-su7 chong2-si7 tioh8 oa2-kho3 Siong7-te3, ng3-